title: (FIRST MONTH FREE) Brand New, Scenic, and Quiet! Affordable Luxury!
posting_body: ['**First full month free.', 'Prorated monthly rent after 1 month free is $1,375.', 'This Unit even had a small yard!', '**', "If you're looking for a brand new, quiet, scenic and downright beautiful new apartment home then look no further!", 'This community has some seriously excellent panoramic views of Austin and its rolling hills.', 'These apartments have 9 foot ceilings, hardwood floors, a washer/dryer in the unit, a spacious balcony (or yard) and a large walk in closet!', 'If you spend a lot of time in the kitchen, you will be working with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops throughout and a extra deep kitchen sink!', 'This apartment home is hosting a impressive amount of onsite amenities including a large 24-hour gym, dog parks, pet washing stations, java bars, outdoor fire side lounge and a signature swimming pool with covered cabanas!', '* 2/2s starting at $1,333 & 3/2s starting at $1,901*', 'Call/text Trent', 'to check it out today.', 'Trent Guerra', 'Apartment Locator + Sales Manager', 'Apartment Hunters LLC', '(8 1 7) 9 9 9-8 8 2 9', "** As a full-time apartment locator I will work day and night to help you find the perfect apartment here in the beautiful Austin Tx, my service is completely FREE to you so please don't hesitate and call me today!", 'Check out our Apartment Hunters Facebook and Google pages to see over one hundred 5 star reviews written from past clients and their experience with me!', '**']
